  fhir:ImplementationGuide.description [ fhir:value "A draft IG representing the human oversight decision over agentic clinical AI output as first-class FHIR resources. Complementary to the HL7 AI Transparency on FHIR IG: that effort represents AI influence on clinical data; this profile represents the human decision (accept/edit/reject, with a structured reason) over agentic AI output."] ;
